name: Fly By (Gameved)
description:
Fly By is a simple game inspired from flappy bird . In this game you play as a pilot of a jet you have to avoid pillar like obstacles .With time the difficulty level of the game increases hence making it a challenge for the player to score a better high score than they did earlier. 

Also don't forget to have a look at my  YouTube channel Gameved(https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwZvhszmXmx_-f0X8qc3Dlw/featured) 

 It's a channel dedicated towards making game and game dev related interesting content.
